expression.expression: CASE WHEN LOWER(TRIM(PRRCDJ)) IS NULL OR TRIM(PRRCDJ) = '' OR TRIM(PRRCDJ) = '0' THEN NULL ELSE to_timestamp(date_add(cast(substring(PRRCDJ + 1900000,1,4) AS Date),cast(substring(PRRCDJ,4,3) as int)-1)) end

CASE WHEN LOWER(TRIM(PRUPMJ)) IS NULL OR TRIM(PRUPMJ) = '' OR TRIM(PRUPMJ) = '0' THEN NULL ELSE to_timestamp(concat(substring(CAST(date_add(concat(substring(CAST(CAST(TRIM(PRUPMJ) AS INT) + 1900000 as string),1,4),'-01-01'), CAST(substring(CAST(CAST(TRIM(PRUPMJ) AS INT) + 1900000 AS string),5,8) AS INT )-1) AS string), 1, 10),' ', lpad(TRIM(PRTDAY), 6, '0')), 'yyyy-MM-dd HHmmss') END

CASE WHEN LOWER(TRIM(SDADDJ)) IS NULL OR TRIM(SDADDJ) = '' OR TRIM(SDADDJ) = '0' THEN NULL ELSE to_timestamp(date_add(cast(substring(SDADDJ + 1900000,1,4) AS Date),cast(substring(SDADDJ,4,3) as int)-1)) end
